        {
          "chunk_id": "DOC-0BCE2319:p1:c0",
          "document_id": "DOC-0BCE2319",
          "content": "1. Overview\nAsset ID: P-101\nType: Main Centrifugal Pump\nLocation: Unit 4",
          "page_number": 1,
          "chunk_index": 0
        },
        {
          "chunk_id": "DOC-0BCE2319:p1:c1",
          "document_id": "DOC-0BCE2319",
          "content": "2. Maintenance Schedule\n- **Monthly:** Check vibration levels at the main bearing casing. Normal threshold < 2.5 mm/s.\n- **Quarterly:** Inspect mechanical seals for leakage. \n- **Annually:** Complete overhaul and alignment check.",
          "page_number": 1,
          "chunk_index": 1
        },
        {
          "chunk_id": "DOC-0BCE2319:p1:c2",
          "document_id": "DOC-0BCE2319",
          "content": "3. Troubleshooting\n- **High Vibration:** Often caused by bearing wear or cavitation. If vibration exceeds 5.0 mm/s, immediately shut down the pump to prevent catastrophic bearing failure.\n- **Seal Leakage:** Can be caused by improper installation or fluid contamination. Replace seals immediately.",
          "page_number": 1,
          "chunk_index": 2
        },
        {
          "chunk_id": "DOC-0BCE2319:p1:c3",
          "document_id": "DOC-0BCE2319",
          "content": "4. Compliance\nAll inspections must be logged in Maximo. Any failure to inspect quarterly results in a Level 2 Compliance Violation.",
          "page_number": 1,
          "chunk_index": 3
        }
      ],
