          "chunk_id": "DOC-2829221C:p1:c0",
          "document_id": "DOC-2829221C",
          "content": "# Shift Log: June 15, 2026\nOperator: Bob\nUnit: 4\n\n08:00 - Started shift. All units running normally.\n09:15 - Noticed unusual noise coming from P-101. \n09:30 - Checked P-101. Casing temperature is elevated. Vibration reading is 4.2 mm/s, which is high but below the shutdown threshold.\n10:00 - Logged observation in Maximo (Ticket #8821). Monitoring closely.\n14:00 - P-101 vibration spiked to 5.8 mm/s. Immediate shutdown initiated.\n14:15 - Maintenance team called. Preliminary inspection shows main bearing failure.\n15:00 - Shift ended. Handed over to Alice. P-101 remains offline.",
          "page_number": 1,
          "chunk_index": 0
        }
